description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 294 private residential units, 676 sq m retail floorspace at ground level facing Woodberry Grove, associated amenity space, underground car parking and cycle parking as well as the enhancement of the Metropolitan Open Land (MOL) area to the south of the blocks adjacent to the New River. The scheme comprises the erection of four blocks ranging in height from 4 storeys to 10 storeys. (Conditions 5, 6, 14, 25, 38, 40, 43 and 45 refer)
